{"tid":763762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高學歷廢青巴打請入] 土匪狆蟈洗腦方法","createTime":"2018-08-01T11:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T01:45:55.000Z","uid":195944,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46dc1f31aa9490b5c656cfe6eee052d231dcb4fd","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"見到巴打開咗個post, 有一隻方法令人討論唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫whataboutism <br />\n簡單講就係將原本要討<br />\n論嘅問題帶去其他更差嘅事上面<br />\n變咗個重點就俾人帶走<br />\n<br />\n例如： 要討論MTR服務好差<br />\n跟著有人就話英國更差 唔見你講？<br />\n如果你同佢爭論英國 香港邊一個服務更差 <br />\n咁你就中伏喇<br />\n<br />\n依個時候你只要唔理佢<br />\n或者一句人地差關香港人咩事呀？<br />\n咁就收佢地皮<br />\n<br />\n高學歷廢青巴打或者其他高手, 土匪仲有無咩洗腦方法俾我地香港人警覺下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？ 想學野<br />\n<br />\n最好俾例子, 理論歷史個啲就唔駛<br />\n因為越簡單我地越易理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a27db9c84e4a5be4d2ff228797808f93f643435","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"最好加埋破解方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929eebff01fc9fa599410d60076fa5003579fac5","tid":763762,"uid":115579,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"中國政府好撚黑暗啊，支：屌 美國咪一樣"},{"pid":"9e4c35ec47c765b02237fbb9382da0d13be360f0","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"929eebff01fc9fa599410d60076fa5003579fac5","tid":763762,"uid":115579,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"中國政府好撚黑暗啊，支：屌 美國咪一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"唔駛理狆蟈口交部啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653e212fed2e3344cf700829c3d7dcf406b09a39","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"廢巴去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？？"},{"pid":"0b4b37dbfcf84310e5582b344fbdbfec78b957cc","tid":763762,"uid":131691,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"你睇返我個archive啦<br />\n已經講咗幾個<br />\n如果你想自己讀住先嘅，可以上Wikipedia讀下以下幾個做入門概論：propaganda techniques, propaganda in Soviet Russia, propaganda in People's Republic of China, 同埋active measures"},{"pid":"29345cf6ed3426fa753df48aec760c2a8c8d2628","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"仲有一個常見手法<br />\n相信權威 屈服權威<br />\n香港人自稱高學歷<br />\n但就豬咁蠢<br />\n唔識分析事情 只要單新聞話有消息指 有學者相信。。。<br />\n咁香港人就信到十足十<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例子： 上次新聞就搵咗個白人  話美國係貿易戰中損失慘重<br />\n個白人其實係所謂分析員 評論家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想講 我同你都係評論家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係科學世界 一啲學者嘅意見係最cheap嘅證據<br />\n無做過一啲嚴緊實驗得出黎嘅證據都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n所以你屋企人信cctvb啲所謂學者 不如信你<br />\n你只要講啲更加高深嘅terms 搞到佢地係明同唔明之間<br />\n咁你就成功咗一半 要不斷重複 只要cctvb一講學者<br />\n你就不斷騷擾你屋企人 時間耐咗 佢地就會對cctvb反感<br />\n<br />\n對付洗腦 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1c3fddf3e3eddf6cff2f05f13af229a988a273","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b4b37dbfcf84310e5582b344fbdbfec78b957cc","tid":763762,"uid":131691,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"你睇返我個archive啦<br />\n已經講咗幾個<br />\n如果你想自己讀住先嘅，可以上Wikipedia讀下以下幾個做入門概論：propaganda techniques, propaganda in Soviet Russia, propaganda in People's Republic of China, 同埋active measures"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以抄啲出黎做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ef2c1afb31f351b1bf556337ba8a6a86fc74ea","tid":763762,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b4b37dbfcf84310e5582b344fbdbfec78b957cc","tid":763762,"uid":131691,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"你睇返我個archive啦<br />\n已經講咗幾個<br />\n如果你想自己讀住先嘅，可以上Wikipedia讀下以下幾個做入門概論：propaganda techniques, propaganda in Soviet Russia, propaganda in People's Republic of China, 同埋active measures"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc9d3e0677cbbf71cd31f9227d8b56b5266661","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"仲有依家中小學啲咩咩團 青年團都係洗腦嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地有好多活動 唔會特別宣傳狆共有幾好<br />\n反而會俾好多野你地學 去狆蟈交流<br />\n等你地慢慢深信狆蟈依家一片太平 發展欣欣向榮<br />\n又或者上堂集會時請好多所謂成功人士 等你地羡慕<br />\n<br />\n破解方法<br />\n連登都有好多中小學生<br />\n你地係比較醒目嘅一群<br />\n如果有依啲團<br />\n你地一定要入去<br />\n攞晒佢地嘅福利<br />\n順便向蠢同學講下香港嘅政事<br />\n一石二鳥就係最終目標<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好俾人引導<br />\n記得狆蟈係無好人 人人都自私自利 只會為自己著想<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d8202811baa156360f2cacc84db0f22a479ad0","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"仲有咩洗腦方法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉移視線<br />\n基本上日日都係發生<br />\n<br />\n例如發生咗一件大新聞 會導致政府出糗嘅或者拆唔掂嘅<br />\n第二日就會爆咗啲關於民生嘅新聞出黎<br />\n大家包括連登仔都會轉到新嘅新聞上面<br />\n如果政府係民生問題解決得好 咁更加會幫手加分<br />\n當件嚴重嘅大新聞完全無發生過咁<br />\n<br />\n破解方法： 無<br />\n香港人係金魚黎<br />\n三秒記憶<br />\n唯有好心人過一段時間就整啲總結出黎<br />\n紀錄底政府有咩衰野<br />\n<br />\n只想同港共講一句 賣港係要還<br />\n只係時辰未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495f540fd05b0e88b841235f7bc1b13782df4837","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a66a12bcca79e55bfe2de33f211ba109be31b07","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c59a32d522057c916016c88462c92531e806f1","tid":763762,"uid":174493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"成個連登周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最常見就係轉移視線/有大單野就唔報導用其他野蓋過本身件事既迴響<br />\n<br />\n再者就係老美最叻既抹黑/膠化，搵一大堆相近case變到趣味可笑&gt;笑完就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n老共有招係扮演敵方做一系列反感事黎影響大眾情緒"},{"pid":"74a1bb31b0953dc42d62eceb71d3d63e61c24a48","tid":763762,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c59a32d522057c916016c88462c92531e806f1","tid":763762,"uid":174493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"成個連登周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最常見就係轉移視線/有大單野就唔報導用其他野蓋過本身件事既迴響<br />\n<br />\n再者就係老美最叻既抹黑/膠化，搵一大堆相近case變到趣味可笑&gt;笑完就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n老共有招係扮演敵方做一系列反感事黎影響大眾情緒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:51:02.000Z",